                <div class="text-center text-lg-left ml-xl-4">
                    <h4 class="mb-4">hi there!</h4>
                    <p class="text-dark" style="font-size: 15px">
                        Welcome to SkinSeoul! Founded in 2001, we started with a simple mission:
                        <em>to bring the best of Korean skincare to you, helping our community achieve healthy, glowing skin</em>.<br />
                        Our journey began in the heart of Prishtina, and since then, we've grown into a beloved destination
                        for skincare enthusiasts, offering a curated selection of premium products and expert advice.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section>
        <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-start">
            <div class="col-lg-6 p-0">
                <img class="img-fluid" src="~/Content/assets/img/about-2.png" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 p-5 py-lg-0" style="max-width: 560px">
                <div class="text-center text-lg-left ml-xl-5">
                    <h4 class="mb-4">our team</h4>
                    <p class="text-dark" style="font-size: 15px">
                        Our team includes licensed estheticians and skincare specialists who stay at the forefront of the latest trends and
                        research in the industry.<br /> With years of experience, they carefully curate our product selection, ensuring that every item
                        meets our high standards for quality and effectiveness. Their deep understanding of skin types and concerns allows them
                        to provide tailored recommendations that cater to your unique needs.
                    </p>
