            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section>
        <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-between">
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2 p-0">
                <img class="img-fluid" src="~/Content/assets/img/about-3.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 p-5 py-lg-0" style="max-width: 560px">
                <div class="text-center text-lg-left ml-xl-4">
                    <h4 class="mb-4">glow essentials</h4>
                    <p class="text-dark" style="font-size: 15px">
                        We offer a thoughtfully curated collection of premium Korean skincare products.
